summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of 13th Ave. from East Fir Street to East Yesler Way, and certain other streets, avenues and alleys, by paving and otherwise improving the same as authorized by Ordinance No. 91938 creating Local Improvement District No. 6281; eliminating the title street from said local improvement district and amending Sections 1 & 2 of said ordinances.
